2026-05-21T11:43:18.7536573Z Description:
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7537455Z libde265 is an open source implementation of the h.265 video codec. It is written from scratch and has a plain C API to enable a simple integration into other software.
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7538361Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7539903Z libde265 supports WPP and tile-based multithreading and includes SSE optimizations. The decoder supports all features of the Main and Main10 profile (HEVC-V1) and most profiles of HEVC-V2 (chroma 4:2:2, 4:4:4, monochrome, and bit depths up to 14 bits).
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7541300Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7541600Z libde265 is released under the LGPL, further information are available at
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7542154Z http://www.libde265.org
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7542511Z https://github.com/strukturag/libde265
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7542789Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7543004Z This PPA contains Ubuntu packages of the libde265 library.
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7543421Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7544395Z Plugins for the GStreamer framework, VLC and required dependencies are only provided for older versions of Ubuntu and are no longer maintained since the libde265 plugin is part of upstream GStreamer.
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7545544Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7545737Z The (old) GStreamer plugin source is available at
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7546232Z https://github.com/strukturag/gstreamer-libde265
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7546597Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7546800Z The VLC plugin source is available at
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7547236Z https://github.com/strukturag/vlc-libde265
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7547534Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7547701Z You can get sample Matroska streams from
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7548179Z http://www.libde265.org/downloads-videos/
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7548627Z http://www.divx.com/de/hevc
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7549209Z http://labs.divx.com/node/127909
2026-05-21T11:43:18.7549771Z More info: https://launchpad.net/~strukturag/+archive/ubuntu/libde265
