2026-05-21T11:43:25.2116350Z Description:
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2116675Z This PPA contains packages to add support for HEIC / HEIF and AVIF files.
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2116969Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2117236Z libheif is an ISO/IEC 23008-12:2017 HEIF and AVIF (AV1 Image File Format) file format decoder and encoder.
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2117596Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2118041Z HEIF and AVIF are new image file formats employing HEVC (h.265) or AV1 image coding, respectively, for the best compression ratios currently possible.
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2118574Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2119319Z libheif makes use of libde265 for HEIF image decoding and x265 for encoding. For AVIF, libaom, dav1d, or rav1e are used as codecs.
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2119802Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2119893Z libheif has support for decoding
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2120117Z - tiled images
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2120306Z - alpha channels
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2120474Z - thumbnails
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2120653Z - reading EXIF and XMP metadata
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2120882Z - reading the depth channel
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2121091Z - multiple images in a file
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2121365Z - image transformations (crop, mirror, rotate)
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2121626Z - overlay images
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2121932Z - plugin interface to add alternative codecs for additional formats (AVC, JPEG)
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2122513Z - decoding of files while downloading (e.g. extract image size before file has been completely downloaded)
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2122973Z - reading color profiles
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2123195Z - heix images (10 and 12 bit, chroma 4:2:2)
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2123379Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2123456Z The encoder supports:
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2123674Z - lossy compression with adjustable quality
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2123919Z - lossless compression
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2124119Z - alpha channels
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2124287Z - thumbnails
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2124467Z - save multiple images to a file
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2124688Z - save EXIF and XMP metadata
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2124906Z - writing color profiles
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2125116Z - 10 and 12 bit images
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2125875Z - monochrome images
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2126123Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2126317Z See https://github.com/strukturag/libheif for further information.
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2126592Z 
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2126755Z NOTE: You might also need to enable the PPA "strukturag/libde265",
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2127091Z so dependencies can be resolved.
2026-05-21T11:43:25.2127414Z More info: https://launchpad.net/~strukturag/+archive/ubuntu/libheif
